short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Quokkr extension relies on a web app that facilitates the exchange of shipping quotes between LTL carriers and their clients.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Quokkr extension works alongside and in support of quokkr.com which is a web application that facilitates the exchange of shipping quotes between LTL trucking carriers and their clients.
